Uses of Class
net.bytebuddy.instrumentation.InvokeDynamic

  • Packages that use InvokeDynamic 
    Package Description
    net.bytebuddy.instrumentation
    The instrumentation package contains any logic for intercepting method calls.

    • Uses of InvokeDynamic in net.bytebuddy.instrumentation

      Subclasses of InvokeDynamic in net.bytebuddy.instrumentation 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      static class  InvokeDynamic.WithImplicitArguments
      Representation of an InvokeDynamic instrumentation where the bootstrapped method is passed a this reference, if available, and any arguments of the instrumented method.
      static class  InvokeDynamic.WithImplicitTarget
      Representation of an InvokeDynamic instrumentation where the bootstrapped method is passed a this reference, if available, and any arguments of the instrumented method and where the invocation target is implicit.
